      "span_text": "A previous study has demonstrated the activation of the MAPK-ERK and PI3-K/AKT survival pathways in immortalized and primary rat brain ECs upon treatment with CM derived from human melanoma cells.  These signaling events contributed to an increase in proliferative and migratory responses of ECs and could be attenuated with specific pathway inhibitors."
